<br>
Sullon Population is to low. People have flooded us cheating with legends gear and &quot;under the table&quot; full gear moves already. Even more people coming to the server would make little difference. <br>
<br>
Opening Sullon and the lesser PvP servers to all servers would let those on other servers do something after they are tired of the PvE game.<br>
<br>
We have our 20percent exp bonus to compensate for our leveling problems anyway.<br>
<br>
And of course the big plus would be that I could actually blast Furor into the dirt and settle any argument as to who is better.<br>
<br>
I just don’t see a lot of down side anymore. Surly if none complain VI be happy to allow server moves for a reasonable &quot;administrative fee&quot;. <br>
<br>
What you all thinks?<br>
