<br>
People who already don't play on PvP, are not very likely to transfer.  For the most part, I see transfers off PvP (one of them actually, left Rallos in 2002).<br>
<br>
PvE content is huge - only a very small percentage of people on servers are elemental-flagged.   VT remains off limits to roughly 95% of EQ players - so there's a lot of stuff to work for.<br>
<br>
