<br>
Everquest was set up as a blue game and I prefer it that way.<br>
<br>
So, should there be gear included movement between servers?  No, I don't think so...especially to a PvP server.  Even a modest blue guild can get HoT armor.  Seems like this would be quite hard on a PvP server.<br>
<br>
My suggestion?  Play a PvP dominated game.  I think you would find it more rewarding.  Do I think you could burn down Furor?  Nope.  I think more likely you would get owned by having his Plane of Time capable buttocks on your server.<br>
